<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zion tang leh van Aksi hawih,
 Lalpa'n kei di'n a siem;
 Dan le ziegam chu ka tun tieng,
 Kipahna pak lun ding.

[V2]
 Hun bang ahimin tuhin ei nang,
 Thisan zieka keia Zion tang;
 Aw bangtik tak leh ka mu ta dem?
 Hukdampa leh gam nitum ngeilo.

[V3]
 2. Tuhin buoina Jordan luipang,
 Ah ka ngak Hukdampa;
 Aksi khel gamnuom chawlh na chu:
 Bangtik leh ka tung dem?

[V4]
 3. Phat nang chiehin, Zion chaten.
 Gam lopi ka ngaklah;
 Ka lenna gamthip gam ahi,
 Taihsan vak ding kei tai.

[V5]
 4. Aw galhat Lal Immanuel,
 Gam chu ka tun tieng leh;
 Hehpihna lal puon thieng silhin,
 Kumsawt in leng tangka.</lyrics>
<title>Van Aksi Hawih</title>
<hymn_number>195</hymn_number>
<author>Patea</author>
</song>